Build Tools: A Hasty Overview Front-end build tools allow us to transpile, bundle, and optimize assets in various ways.
Now, technically, webpack is a module bundler and doesn&rsquo;t quite fit in with Gulp and Grunt, which are &ldquo;task runners,&rdquo; but since there is great overlap in the functionality offered by each tool, I&rsquo;ll just refer to them all collectively as &ldquo;build tools.&rdquo;
Grunt came first - let&rsquo;s start with that.
